snippet.title: Yard Sale Simulator | Trailer
snippet.description:
Yard Sale Simulator is releasing November 30th 2023!
For more info visit our Steam page
Wishlist to show support
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416350/Yard_Sale_Simulator/

Follow me on #twitter https://twitter.com/QueenfishGames

An open world yard sale simulator. Buy, repair and sell your way to the top. Shop yard sales, hold your own yard sale, buy a market stand, upgrade your stand or open a shop in town to sell all your newly acquired valuables.
